 美分和迪迪。图片来源：杰米·麦卡锡 (Jamie McCarthy) 和加雷斯·卡特莫尔 (Gareth Cattermole)，来源：GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/50-Cent-and-Diddy.-Credit-Jamie-McCarthy-and-Gareth-Cattermole-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/50-Cent-and-Diddy.-Credit-Jamie-McCarthy-and-Gareth-Cattermole-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/50-Cent-and-Diddy.-Credit-Jamie-McCarthy-and-Gareth-Cattermole-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/50-Cent-and-Diddy.-Credit-Jamie-McCarthy-and-Gareth-Cattermole-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/50-Cent-and-Diddy.-Credit-Jamie-McCarthy-and-Gareth-Cattermole-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/50-Cent-and-Diddy.-Credit-Jamie-McCarthy-and-Gareth-Cattermole-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artist/50-cent">50 Cent</a>声称<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Netflix</a>已经选择了他关于<a href="/artists/diddy">吹牛老爹</a>的纪录片，这家流媒体巨头赢得了“竞购战”。</p><p>吹牛老爹（Diddy）——真名肖恩·库姆斯（Sean Combs）——目前正面临一系列有关性贩运、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sean-diddy-combs-accused-of-sexual-harassment-and-assault-by-music-producer-3593467">性侵犯和性骚扰</a>指控的持续调查。这位说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sean-diddy-combs-homes-raided-sex-trafficking-investigation-3609464">在迈阿密和洛杉矶的住所于三月份遭到搜查</a>，似乎与这些指控有关。这位“我会想念你”的歌手否认了所有针对他的指控。</p><p>早在三月份，50 Cent 就证实将发行一部<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/50-cent-confirms-docu-series-on-diddys-sexual-assault-allegations-3610304">关于库姆斯性侵犯指控的纪录片</a>，名为<i>《吹牛老爹？》（Diddy Do It？）</i></p><p>现在，50 Cent（真名柯蒂斯·杰克逊）透露，Netflix 已经购买了他关于吹牛老爹性侵犯指控的多集纪录片。</p><p>这位《糖果店》说唱歌手声称，即将推出的纪录片系列存在一场“竞标战”，该系列纪录片由他的娱乐公司 G-Unit 影视制作。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C7QHoMyND